{"tid":997214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【男公關奢華慶生】涉事白馬會所被查封　高帥「男模」日薪達1萬","createTime":"2019-01-27T03:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T09:04:42.000Z","uid":12558,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1b17c61ed6029e836549077e7b2c585a37ff2155","tid":997214,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"近日內地網上流傳，上海白馬會所有男公關獲「富婆」餽贈貴重禮物以慶祝28歲生日，價值以百萬元（人民幣．下同）計，引起公眾關注。<br />\n事件曝光後，白馬會所疑似為免惹上麻煩，在官方微博刪除大量貼文。不過有內媒於1月26日引述公安消息，指白馬會所「已經沖掉了」，「已經抓掉了」。<br />\n<br />\n內地《北京青年報》26日報道，上海市靜安分局南京西路派出所回應查詢，透露公安昨天（25日）已「依法處理」位於旺旺大廈的白馬會所：「白馬會所昨天已經沖掉了，昨天已經被抓掉了。」旺旺大廈的工作人員亦證實消息，指該會所現已停止營業。<br />\n<br />\n《北青報》又引述自稱是白馬會所前員工的消息人士，指網傳的「過生日事件」屬實。<br />\n<br />\n一次過補齊1歲到28歲生日<br />\n<br />\n上海著名女性娛樂場所「白馬會所」日前被爆料，稱有一名男公關舉行派對，慶祝28歲生日，其間獲「富婆」贈送包括Audi豪車及28萬元現金在內的生日禮物。<br />\n<br />\n爆料網民指，「富婆」一共送給該名男公關28份生日禮物，一次過補齊從1歲到28歲，每份禮物上都有寫明是第幾歲的禮物。其中28歲的生日禮物就是總值28萬元的現金，以及象徵愛情一輩子的純金杯，至於27歲的生日禮物就是一輛Audi豪車。<br />\n<br />\n不少人月入高達8萬元<br />\n<br />\n白馬會所位於上海靜安區，據傳小費至少要1000元，會所內的男公關身高都1.8米或以上，且外形靚仔、有型、陽光，其中不少人月入高達8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n目前疑似白馬會所官網仍可供瀏覽，官方介紹該會所原名「完美空間」，「被譽為亞洲時尚女性的伊甸園」。據其2018年10月所載「招聘男模」廣告所示，入職要求為身高180cm以上，「五官要特別帥」，「穿著時尚有品位（味）」，每一班日薪1000至10000元不等，小費更「上不封頂」，每日結算。<br />\n<br />\n該則招聘廣告亦注明「訂房價目表」：小房間（6至8人）最低消費是3770元；大房間（8至10人）最低消費是7700元；VIP大房間最低消費是15700元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcfHKQd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcfHKQd.png&h=be1a9144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kY9UAWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkY9UAWU.png&h=9f3df5eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywKdRve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywKdRve.png&h=ac323eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSz9pQf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSz9pQf.png&h=c61be3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSO2KQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSO2KQg.png&h=7cce4a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gLsVWW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gLsVWW.png&h=a7c4812e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuHV4Qh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuHV4Qh.png&h=45ef0f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTDqHBX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTDqHBX.png&h=7ba02fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gYqHBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gYqHBY.png&h=250a6839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVM7VWY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVM7VWY.png&h=4fdcba6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ed6f438709feaab28f87b252dd882a08b114002","tid":997214,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"真係幾靚仔喎"},{"pid":"db51facda0efd617dd476157f04591458776241f","tid":997214,"uid":121473,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8BzAYX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8BzAYX.png&h=6a8555f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a07e0d39b490c14768a0f7f0afbf25028b9a36c","tid":997214,"uid":136662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"db51facda0efd617dd476157f04591458776241f","tid":997214,"uid":121473,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8BzAYX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8BzAYX.png&h=6a8555f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"就嚟要叫gay登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11